CREATE TABLE retirement_transactions (
  transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  account_id INT,
  transaction_type VARCHAR(10),
  amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  transaction_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    account_id INT,
    transaction_date DATE,
    amount DECIMAL,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
  transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  account_id INT,
  transaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  amount DECIMAL,
  transaction_date DATE
);
